                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Enterprise IT Solutions Consulting</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Providing strategic technology guidance to align your IT infrastructure with your core business objectives.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Service Card 2 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-4">
                            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Enterprise Web Hosting</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Reliable, secure, and high-performance hosting solutions tailored for enterprise-level traffic and applications.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Service Card 3 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-4">
                            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Website SEO</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Enhancing your visibility on search engines to attract more organic traffic and qualified leads.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Service Card 4 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-4">
                            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Site Performance Optimization</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Dramatically improving your website's loading speed for a better user experience and higher conversions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Service Card 5 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-4">
                            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" xmlns="http://wwwwww.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Website Data Analytics</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Uncovering valuable insights from your website data to make informed, strategic business decisions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Service Card 6 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-4">
                            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Website Architecture Design</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Building scalable, secure, and robust technical foundations for your web applications.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
        <section id="why-us" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-gray-50">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="text-center mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Why Partner With bits.kittle?</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-600">We deliver more than just code. We deliver a competitive advantage.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="space-y-10">
                        <div class="flex">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white">
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Deeply Integrated Partnership</h3>
                                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We don't just build, we embed. By deeply understanding your business model from day one, we design and deliver truly customized solutions that function as a natural extension of your team.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white">
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" /></svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">World-Class Technical Expertise</h3>
                                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Gain a decisive advantage with leadership from a <strong class="text-gray-800">Stanford University graduate</strong> with over <strong class="text-gray-800">20 years of experience</strong> architecting and building solutions at the world's top tech and Fortune 500 companies.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <img class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="A diverse team of professionals collaborating in a modern office.">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Values Section -->
        <section id="values" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-blue-600 text-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="text-center mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold">Our Values</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-blue-200">The principles that guide our partnership with you.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Client Success is Our Metric</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-blue-100">We go beyond deliverables. We measure our success by the tangible value and business growth we create for you. Your goals are our goals.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Bias for Action</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-blue-100">We are proactive, agile, and results-driven. We believe in rapid execution and iterative improvement to deliver value quickly and efficiently.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Partnership Built on Trust</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-blue-100">Transparency, clear communication, and unwavering reliability are the cornerstones of our client relationships. We are your dedicated partner, every step of the way.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Story Section -->
        <section id="our-story" class="py-20 sm:py-28">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="relative flex justify-center items-center">
                        <div class="absolute w-4/5 h-4/5 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg transform -rotate-6"></div>
                        <img class="relative rounded-lg shadow-xl w-4/5" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573865526739-10659fec78a5?q=80&w=1915&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="A cute cat named Skittles, the inspiration for the company name.">
                    </div>
                    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
                        <div class="mt-6 bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">The Inspiration Behind Our Name</h3>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                People often ask about our name. "bits.kittle" is inspired by a beloved cat named Skittles. To us, Skittles represents the perfect blend of agility, reliability, and approachabilityâ€”qualities we embed into every project. We combine the technical precision of "bits" with the friendly, dependable spirit of "kittle" to build technology that not only works, but works for you.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Final CTA Section -->
        <section id="contact" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-gray-50">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Ready to Elevate Your Digital Presence?</h2>
                <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-600">
                    Let's discuss how our expertise can help you achieve your business goals. Reach out today for a no-obligation consultation.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-10">
                    <a href="mailto:contact@bitskittle.com" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
                        Contact Us
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300">
        <div class="container mx-auto py-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-xl font-bold">bits.kittle<span class="text-blue-500">.</span></p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Serving a global clientele with partners across North America and China.</p>
            <div class="my-4 border-t border-gray-700 w-1/4 mx-auto"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">&copy; 2025 bits.kittle Inc. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>